rComments: Weekly assignments: reading and  answering a groupe of questions in a form she gives. These questions need zero analyze, much as a secondary school level reading. I got an A+ without great effort. She makes you buy the book she wrote, which you will use it only for a couple of weeks of the course. No groupe projects or discussion.

Carole assigns weekly assignments. Her course plan is very detailed and specific but easy to follow. Her criteria is clear. You do need to read a lot and listen to her recordings but the questions and the assignments are easy if you keep on top. Its an easy A!
